<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 6" captionStartId="F6" captionText="Figure 6. Cytospora myrtagena on Castanea mollissima (BJFC-S 1704). A, B Habit of conidiomata on branches C, E transverse section of conidiomata D longitudinal section through conidiomata F, G conidiogenous cells attached with conidia H conidia. Scale bars: 500 μm (B-D), 5 μm (E, G), 10 μm (H)." figureDoi="10.3897/mycokeys.62.47425.figure6" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/371657" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Figure 6</figureCitation>
